    "title" : "LWJGL cannot use glGenVertexArrays()",
    "body" : "<p>I am just trying to create a 3d game with LWJGL on my mac, but when I tried to use <code>GL30.glGenVertexArrays();</code></p>\n<p>It does not work, and gives an error:<br />\n<code>FATAL ERROR in native method: Thread[#1,main,5,main]: No context is current or a function that is not available in the current context was called. The JVM will abort execution.</code></p>\n<p>I had already placed these two lines of code:</p>\n<pre><code>GLFW.glfwMakeContextCurrent(window);\nGL.createCapabilities();\n</code></pre>\n<p>Before using this</p>\n<pre><code>GL30.glGenVertexArrays();\n</code></pre>\n<p>It still did not work. Can you give any suggestions or any help?</p>\n",
